doctype html
html
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=edge')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='main.css')
    // once set, the styles need to be included in a <style> tag. after that, use the CSS inline styles tool. copy and replace the outputed "body" portion, and deleted the <style> tag when ready to send.
  body
    .email-wrapper
      .header
        h1 Textrade    
      .formality
        p
           | {month day, year} <br/>
           | {subject} 
           // in this case, the subject would be "account verification
      .message 
        h2 Hi {firstName}
        p.intro Welcom to Textrade! We're excited to have you. Before you can start renting and trading on Textrade you'll have to veryify your account. To do so, simply click the link bellow, or let us know if you're having a problem. 
        a.verification Click here to veryify your account
        p.close Thank you for choosing to use Textrade, an educated book buying market.
      .footer
        p.unsubscribe We know, it's not you, it's us. If you'd like us to give you some space just <a>unsubscribe</a>.
        